[SPEAKER_01] naspirali.

399
00:27:54,759 --> 00:27:57,579
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu stvari u našem predanju.

400
00:27:57,579 --> 00:27:58,740
[SPEAKER_01] Papa Ivacem treći

401
00:27:58,740 --> 00:28:00,319
[SPEAKER_01] tu jedan od najsvetovnijih papa.

402
00:28:00,319 --> 00:28:01,859
[SPEAKER_01] I kada je vidio Franju

403
00:28:01,859 --> 00:28:03,160
[SPEAKER_01] rekao mu je

404
00:28:03,160 --> 00:28:04,900
[SPEAKER_01] ajde ti.

405
00:28:04,900 --> 00:28:06,359
[SPEAKER_01] Odmah ne potrebe.

406
00:28:06,359 --> 00:28:08,200
[SPEAKER_01] A Bog mu je dao da sanja sam

407
00:28:08,200 --> 00:28:08,740
[SPEAKER_01] tu noć

408
00:28:08,740 --> 00:28:10,420
[SPEAKER_01] u kojoj se crkva ruši.

409
00:28:10,420 --> 00:28:11,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ovdje stoji na stijeni

410
00:28:11,380 --> 00:28:11,940
[SPEAKER_01] i ruši se

411
00:28:11,940 --> 00:28:13,380
