414
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:16,359
[SPEAKER_01] da ona ne pada.

415
00:28:16,359 --> 00:28:17,440
[SPEAKER_01] I drugi dan ga je pozva

416
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:18,220
[SPEAKER_01] da vam u blagoslov

417
00:28:18,220 --> 00:28:19,180
