420
00:28:22,440 --> 00:28:24,900
[SPEAKER_01] U vam su.

421
00:28:24,900 --> 00:28:27,240
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo pojište

422
00:28:27,240 --> 00:28:27,400
[SPEAKER_01] u kojem trebate

423
00:28:27,400 --> 00:28:28,359
[SPEAKER_01] od radne pobijediti

424
00:28:28,359 --> 00:28:29,099
