430
00:28:37,279 --> 00:28:39,359
[SPEAKER_01] Tenk je prešao preko crkve,

431
00:28:39,359 --> 00:28:40,259
[SPEAKER_01] preko otara.

432
00:28:40,259 --> 00:28:41,779
[SPEAKER_01] A ono što je meni

433
00:28:41,779 --> 00:28:42,400
