440
00:28:52,259 --> 00:28:53,519
[SPEAKER_01] Teški fizički rad.

441
00:28:53,519 --> 00:28:55,200
[SPEAKER_01] I Bog je da odal kapelan

442
00:28:55,200 --> 00:28:55,779
[SPEAKER_01] na toj žubi

443
00:28:55,779 --> 00:28:56,839
[SPEAKER_01] bude svek čoviti.

444
00:28:56,839 --> 00:28:58,440
[SPEAKER_01] I on je vikao

